text:
 Head over to Mt. Shiveer. Click the world map at the bottom right of your screen and go to Mt. Shiveer, which should be around the top left of the map. If you already have a hot cocoa maker in your den, this is optional. Go to the cocoa hut located in Mt. Shiveer. It will be the building with the purple tent-like roof with patches on it. It's located around the bottom left of where you spawn when you go to Mt. Shiveer by map. Again, if you have a hot cocoa maker in your den, that works as well. Click the remote control button beside the hot cocoa making machine. It should be in a floating diamond next to the machine. Click on the cup shape and pattern of your choice. There are 4 different cup shapes and patterns that you can choose from. A wide cup with a handle and a zigzag pattern{"smallUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/b\/be\/Screen-Shot-2018-12-09-at-9.03.54-PM.png\/460px-Screen-Shot-2018-12-09-at-9.03.54-PM.png","bigUrl":"https:\/\/www.wikihow.com\/images\/thumb\/b\/be\/Screen-Shot-2018-12-09-at-9.03.54-PM.png\/759px-Screen-Shot-2018-12-09-at-9.03.54-PM.png","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":273,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":450.989010989011,"licensing":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>License: <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Fair_use\">Fair Use<\/a> (screenshot)<br>\n<\/p><\/div>"}

